==English==

===Noun===
{{en-noun-reg-y|responsibilit|y}}

# The [[act]] of being [[responsible]].
#:'''''Responsibility''' is a heavy burden.''
# A [[duty]] or [[obligation]] for which someone is responsible.
#:''Keeping this system under control is everyone's '''responsibility'''.''
# A [[liability]] that you must take care of.
#:''Why didn't you clean the house?  That was your '''responsibility'''!''

